    <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;">🧐</div>
    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; text-align: center;"><b>As a critique partner:</b></h3>
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14pt; line-height: 1.5;">
      Students learn to spot bias, errors, or poor design in AI outputs, strengthening their critical evaluation skills.
    </p>
  </div>

